              <header class="node-header">

                  <h1 class="node-title" rel="nofollow">
                          Donate to QuestionCopyright.org                      </h1>
        
        
      </header>
        
    <div class="node-content">
        <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden view-mode-full"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><div class="qco-informational" style="text-align: left;">
<p><img src="http://mimiandeunice.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/ME_402_CensorshipVsCopyright1-640x199.png" height="185" width="601" /></p>
<p><a href="http://flattr.com/thing/47980/QuestionCopyright-org" target="_blank"> <img src="http://api.flattr.com/button/flattr-badge-large.png" alt="Flattr this" title="Flattr this" border="0" /></a><br /></p><h2 style="text-align: left;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Donate to QuestionCopyright.org</span></h2>
<p>Your donation supports our existing activities and helps us expand our work.  If you want to give to a specific QCO project, please specify the project's name in the memo line or notes field of your donation.</p>
<div id="paypal" title="paypal">
<div id="credit-card" title="credit-card">
<p style="text-align: left;">By credit card / PayPal:</p>
<blockquote><form style="text-align: left;" action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post"> <input name="cmd" value="_s-xclick" type="hidden" /><input name="hosted_button_id" value="507717" type="hidden" /><input name="submit" src="https://www.paypal.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_donateCC_LG.gif" type="image" /><img src="https://www.paypal.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif" border="0" height="1" width="1" /></form>
</blockquote>
</div>
</div>
<div id="bitcoin" title="bitcoin">
<p style="text-align: left;">or by Bitcoin:</p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><img src="/cm/images/bitcoin.jpg" alt="Bitcoin Logo" style="margin-left: 3em;" /></p>
<p style="text-align: left; margin-left: 3em;">at our Bitcoin address: <span style="font-family: courier new,courier; font-weight: bold;">1EDFgxTaq53N7oz54UZWW36PZDLnvNshkx</span><br /><span style="font-style: italic;">(if you need maximum security and anonymity, please <a href="/contact">contact us</a> to get a one-time Bitcoin address)</span></p>
</div>
<div id="mail" title="mail">
<p style="text-align: left;">or by mail:</p>
<blockquote style="text-align: left;"><p><strong>QuestionCopyright.org<br />P.O. Box 20165<br />Stanford, CA 94309-0165<br />USA </strong></p></blockquote>
</div>
<div id="other" title="other">
<p style="text-align: left;">or <strong><a href="http://questioncopyright.org/contact">contact us</a></strong>, if you'd like to donate by some other means (e.g., direct bank transfer).</p>
</div>
<p><strong><em>A Note About Directed Donations:</em></strong><br /><br />If making a directed donation to a specific purpose or project, please remember to <strong>write the purpose in the memo line or notes field</strong> of your donation. (When donating via PayPal, the notes field is in <em>"Add special instructions to the seller"</em> after logging in.) For example, to donate to the Sita Distribution Project, just write <em>"Sita Distribution Project"</em>.<br /><br />QuestionCopyright.org is a <a href="corporation#501c3">non-profit (501c3)</a> organization, and donations to us are fully tax-deductible to the extent permitted by law.</p>
</div>
